{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, these features provide all aspects of analyzing business needs that are measurable and contributes to the growth of the business.",
    "With these features, we can support different types of companies and provide a well-fitted bias-free model to predict business success using machine learning algorithms.",
    "Business success prediction aims to analyze factors and features responsible for maintaining a profitable business and have a clear business target to produce measurable results.",
    "Analyzing business success is challenging due to unknown business data and fluctuations.",
    "Exploring business features and choosing a well-fitted model based on the company's different business angles and targets is important."
  ]
}